Creator JCP

Title Setup for the 2012 transit of Venus. 6/5/12.

Description The setup for the 2012 transit of Venus, ready to go. The 6-inch reflector is used to project the Sun, while the sun funnel refractor piggybacks on the 12-inch.

Original Date 6/5/12, 7:32 PM

Make Canon

Camera Canon EOS DIGITAL REBEL XT

Focal Length (35mm) 57mm

Metering Mode Multi-segment

ISO Equivalent 400

Exposure Time 1/100s

Aperture ƒ/8.0

Exposure bias 0 EV

Exposure Program Program normal

White balance Auto white balance

Flash Flash did not fire

Resolution 800 x 533
